### Strings

You can pass raw strings to `vars()` and separate them by commas.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
temps %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  data_color(
    columns = vars("Jan", "Feb"),
    colors = hulk_pal
  )
```

