#### Wrapper

Similarly, this could just be a wrapper around `data_color` alone, rather than the full `gt` pipeline.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data_color_cols <- function(gt_data, ..., palette = hulk_pal) {
  gt_data %>%
    data_color(
      columns = vars(...),
      colors = palette
    )
}

temps %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  data_color_cols(Jan, Feb, Mar, Apr, May, Jun)
```

