### Embrace

The embracing operator `{{ }}` can be used for single columns.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
color_column <- function(data_in, column, palette = hulk_pal) {

  data_in %>%
    gt() %>%
    data_color(
      columns = vars({{column}}),
      colors = palette
    )
}

color_columns(temps, Jun)
```

