#### Wrapper

Similarly, this could just be a wrapper around `data_color` alone, rather than the full `gt` pipeline.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
data_color_col <- function(gt_data, column, palette = hulk_pal) {

  gt_data %>%
    data_color(
      columns = vars({{column}}),
      colors = palette
    )
}

temps %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  data_color_col(column = Jun)
```

